snippet.title: 20XX Tournament Edition - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Free on release. Pre-loaded cards available! http://20xx.me
Twitter: http://twitter.com/dansalvato1

20XX Tournament Edition launches in November 2015. A closed beta for TOs will begin July 2015. Apply for the beta on the website.

Special thanks to everyone in the Melee hacking community who have helped make this culmination possible.

Song: The Asteroids Galaxy Tour - Rock the Ride
Some gameplay footage from https://www.youtube.com/user/gamerfreak5665
